CC-BY-4.0 License (for .md files)
---------------------------------
All markdown (.md) files are licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International:
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

When using .md files, you MUST:
1. Retain complete attribution: "Author: ChrisHF" 
2. Include original article URL: "Originally published in [Your Journal Name], available at: [Article URL]"
3. Indicate if modifications were made: "This work is adapted from the original"
4. Include a copy of this license or link to https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/


